These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There 7 different types of food: apricot, raspberry, eggplant, papaya, strawberry, cabbage, asparagus
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, tulip, daffodil, iris, lily, begonia
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating papaya##1
 3. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbegonia and the person eating cabbage##2
 9. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who growsdaisy##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
14. the person eating cabbage is the person who growstulip##1
15. the person who growslily is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Food   | raspberry | papaya         | asparagus   | apricot | cabbage    | strawberry | eggplant |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Flower     | iris  | lily         | daisy     | aconite    | tulip | daffodil     | begonia     |

