 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rabbit and the gothic-revival house##2
11. the owner of the pony is the art-deco house##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the owner of the bird is between the gothic-revival house and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the farmhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
